@UserApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7002

### Bootstrap a user profile (called by AuthService after signup)
POST {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "username": "jdoe",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

###

### Get a user profile by ID
GET {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###

### Update profile (requires Bearer token)
PUT {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Software engineer and traveller.",
  "location": "Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam",
  "websiteUrl": "https://example.com",
  "isPrivate": false
}

###

### Update avatar (requires Bearer token)
POST {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/avatars/jdoe.png"
}

###

### Update cover (requires Bearer token)
POST {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/cover
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coverUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/covers/jdoe.jpg"
}

###

### Follow a user (requires Bearer token)
POST {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Unfollow a user (requires Bearer token)
DELETE {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get followers
GET {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/followers?page=1&pageSize=20

###

### Get following
GET {{UserApi_HostAddress}}/api/userprofiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/following?page=1&pageSize=20
